Diamond::

She went down to the training center and activated a level 10 
training program.  It was one of the toughest training programs the 
center had.

She walked out of the training center two hours later, covered in 
bruises and mechfluid.  She looked like the pit, but she felt a lot 
better.  She walked down the halls, leaving a small trail of fluid.  
She made it to her quarters and got cleaned up.  She smiled, "I think 
thingsss will work out jussst fine."  She called up FZ," Oh great 
leader, what do you have for Diamond to accomplisssh today?"
She knew that you caught more flies with honey than with vinagar, so 
she used a sweet tongue to get FZ to give her a job to do. She wanted 
to kill a maximal. She killed one pred leader, now she wanted another 
victim to play with.
